<span id="freeTextContainer15512727550269166180">Zombies Are Real! 🧟‍♀️<br/><br/>Somebody is plotting an apocalypse! Terrorist are attacking the world! They have created a virus that kills and then re-animate the dead!<br/><br/>The zombies are violent and hungry for human flesh!<br/><br/>Here comes Joe Ledger of the DMS ( Department of Military Science). He and his team are on it. They have the guts to fight the walking dead and kill them and the terrorists!<br/><br/>Will they succeed? Will they stop the apocalypse or will they fail in their mission? <br/><br/>Read this book and find out.</span>

