<div id="review_1279539431" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1279539431" />
    <a title="Cindy Newton" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6082517-cindy-newton"><img alt="Cindy Newton" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1432075684p2/6082517.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1279539431?book_show_action=true">Jan 05, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cindy Newton" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cindy Newton" href="/user/show/6082517-cindy-newton">Cindy Newton</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6082517-cindy-newton?shelf=owned-books">owned-books</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6082517-cindy-newton?shelf=zombies">zombies</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6082517-cindy-newton?shelf=part-of-a-series">part-of-a-series</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6082517-cindy-newton?shelf=audible">audible</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1279539431" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7883032922311143015">I started off 2018 with a zombie book--<i>The Girl With All the Gifts</i>, and I have now started 2019 on the same note. This is a really good read with lots of action and lots of zombies. Joe Ledger is a fun protagonist with a snarky voice and a badass attitude. The explanation for the zombie plague, how it came about and what it is intended for, is a fairly new and unique one and there is some logic to it. The action is intense and non-stop. This is highly recommended for zombie and action fans! I&apos;m </span>
  <span id="freeText7883032922311143015" style="display:none">I started off 2018 with a zombie book--<i>The Girl With All the Gifts</i>, and I have now started 2019 on the same note. This is a really good read with lots of action and lots of zombies. Joe Ledger is a fun protagonist with a snarky voice and a badass attitude. The explanation for the zombie plague, how it came about and what it is intended for, is a fairly new and unique one and there is some logic to it. The action is intense and non-stop. This is highly recommended for zombie and action fans! I'm definitely going to read the next in the series.</span>
  <a data-text-id="7883032922311143015" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


