<span id="freeTextContainer15090498279779961002">Joe Ledger was sent to America to kick platypus ass and kill zombies!! And there ain’t no more platypuses on this continent! So watch it zombies cuz this “man” can kick the shit out of a room full of special forces members in less than 6 seconds!! Yes you read right! 6 seconds, he can make a last stand against dozens and dozens of zombies without even getting a scratch, this man is like the Chuck Norris of zombie slaying!! I swear to god I kept expecting him to grab a zombie by the arms rip em’ </span>
  <span id="freeText15090498279779961002" style="display:none">Joe Ledger was sent to America to kick platypus ass and kill zombies!! And there ain’t no more platypuses on this continent! So watch it zombies cuz this “man” can kick the shit out of a room full of special forces members in less than 6 seconds!! Yes you read right! 6 seconds, he can make a last stand against dozens and dozens of zombies without even getting a scratch, this man is like the Chuck Norris of zombie slaying!! I swear to god I kept expecting him to grab a zombie by the arms rip em’ off and kill another zombie with the severed limbs! That’s how hardcore Joe Ledger is! I keep trying to think of ways of explaining the awesome force that Joe Ledger is… but all I could come up with is this: imagine that you put together on a blender: Achilles’ body + the amazing mankind saving abilities of Keanu Reaves + the balls of Steven Coltbert + the tactician mind of Alexander The Great+ the martial art awesomeness of Chuck Norris … the result of that will be Joe Ledger, there I said it! If there was a zombie outbreak right now on my city and I was forced to ask for one person and only one person to help get thru it… I’ll choose Joe Ledger… a 4 out of 5!!!</span>
