		<td>
		    <b>
          <a title="Benvenuti a Dunwich Horror" class="actionLink" href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show/22118071-gdl-gennaio-2022-gr-choice-award-2011---patient-zero">Benvenuti a Dunwi...:</a>
